313
00:33:58,413 --> 00:33:59,540
Got it?

314
00:34:02,709 --> 00:34:04,545
Who are you?

315
00:34:04,670 --> 00:34:06,630
My name is Lai.
I come from Chi...

316
00:34:06,755 --> 00:34:08,215
Uhh!

317
00:34:08,298 --> 00:34:11,260
I ask the questions.
You answer the questions.

318
00:34:11,385 --> 00:34:12,970
Nothing more.
Nothing less.

319
