321
00:34:20,978 --> 00:34:23,313
Deep shit.
Very deep shit.

322
00:34:23,397 --> 00:34:25,357
Those guys...
Sorry! Sorry!

323
00:34:25,482 --> 00:34:26,692
I won't say any...
Mm!

324
