340
00:37:22,242 --> 00:37:24,161
He's not.

341
00:37:29,666 --> 00:37:31,168
Believe me.

342
00:37:33,545 --> 00:37:35,047
I believe you.

343
00:37:35,172 --> 00:37:39,426
