487
00:45:39,364 --> 00:45:40,240
Uhh!

488
00:45:42,784 --> 00:45:43,702
Aah!

489
00:45:46,622 --> 00:45:47,539
Go! Go! Go!

490
00:45:53,962 --> 00:45:54,880
Uhh!

491
00:45:58,800 --> 00:46:00,886
- Aah!
- Aah!

492
00:46:00,969 --> 00:46:02,012
