496
00:46:31,041 --> 00:46:32,334
Frank!

497
00:46:34,253 --> 00:46:35,671
Come on,
give me your hand!

498
00:46:39,675 --> 00:46:40,926
Aah!

499
00:46:48,016 --> 00:46:49,643
Uhh!

500
00:46:49,768 --> 00:46:51,979
Aah!

501
00:46:59,069 --> 00:47:01,363
- Aah!
- Come on!

502
00:47:03,574 --> 00:47:05,117
Come on, get in!
