I'm coming back.

509
00:47:44,364 --> 00:47:46,658
No, wait! Wait!

510
00:47:51,830 --> 00:47:52,998
Uhh!

511
00:47:56,460 --> 00:47:57,878
Aah!

512
00:47:59,880 --> 00:48:01,507
