513
00:48:04,051 --> 00:48:05,344
- You OK?
- Mm.

514
00:48:05,427 --> 00:48:06,887
Sure?

515
00:48:06,970 --> 00:48:08,555
OK, let's go.

516
00:49:47,988 --> 00:49:50,115
Frank?

517
00:49:50,240 --> 00:49:51,992
Is this your house?

518
00:49:55,412 --> 00:49:56,788
Lai:
Frank?

519
00:49:56,872 --> 00:49:58,749
Uhh! Yeah, guess.

520
00:50:01,376 --> 00:50:03,670
Frank.

521
00:50:10,344 --> 00:50:12,846
I should mind
my own goddamn business.

522
00:50:14,848 --> 00:50:18,143
A simple rule.
A simple, little rule.

523
00:50:18,227 --> 00:50:19,520
There's gotta be
some dry clothes...

524
00:50:19,645 --> 00:50:22,523
in this house.

525
00:50:22,648 --> 00:50:26,068
Don't open the package.

526
00:50:26,151 --> 00:50:27,694
Nothing but trouble,
you open the goddamn package.

527
00:50:29,530 --> 00:50:30,447
Lai:
Frank.

528
00:50:34,618 --> 00:50:35,536
What are you doing?

529
00:50:35,619 --> 00:50:37,371
Making up for the trouble.

530
00:50:43,377 --> 00:50:44,837
Wait, wait.

531
00:50:44,962 --> 00:50:45,879
Why are you making...

532
00:50:46,004 --> 00:50:47,381
No more questions.

533
00:50:49,967 --> 00:50:51,009
Wait.

534
00:50:51,093 --> 00:50:53,053
I don't like it
when things get complicated.

535
00:50:53,136 --> 00:50:55,514
You like things simple.

536
00:50:55,597 --> 00:50:57,224
Very simple.

537
00:51:13,615 --> 00:51:15,325
I'm not so clear
about the house.

538
00:51:15,450 --> 00:51:17,744
Could you explain...

539
00:51:17,870 --> 00:51:20,205
uh, one more time.
After I left.

540
00:51:20,289 --> 00:51:22,291
After you left, we went
for a walk on the beach.

541
00:51:22,374 --> 00:51:23,750
- Had a swim.
- Where again?

542
00:51:23,834 --> 00:51:24,877
Past the point.

543
00:51:25,002 --> 00:51:26,670
Anyone else swimming
at that time?

544
00:51:26,795 --> 00:51:27,671
No.

545
00:51:27,796 --> 00:51:28,964
Did you see
anybody else swimming?

546
00:51:29,089 --> 00:51:30,591
No. No one.

547
00:51:30,716 --> 00:51:35,387
So, you took a walk,
had a swim...

548
00:51:35,470 --> 00:51:37,681
on a beach where no one
else was swimming...

549
00:51:37,806 --> 00:51:40,559
past the point
where you can't see...

550
00:51:40,642 --> 00:51:43,103
or be seen from the beach
on either side...

551
00:51:43,228 --> 00:51:45,939
which makes witnesses
a little hard to come by.

